data.description: Nearly new home, only 2 years old! Marvel at the open great room floor plan downstairs as you entertain family & guests or catch the big game on tv and cook at the same time. The kitchen is outfitted with stainless steel appliances, dark rich wood cabinetry, and an island with sink, garbage disposal, & built-in dishwasher, along with a raised breakfast bar. Vaulted ceilings with recessed lighting throughout and lots of windows fill the room with light. The dining area has a slider to the little back porch and easy low maintenance fully fenced yard, just waiting for your special touch to add onto the deck, add raised garden beds and hanging baskets along the fence line, which will thrive in the Southern exposure, or perhaps make it a dog run. A lovely meadow like yard backs up to the property providing privacy and wonderful views of greenery and both glorious sunrises and sunsets. The hallway has a half bath and door into your large 2 car garage. Then make your way up to the second floor to find the laundry conveniently located at the top of the stairs. The primary suite has it's own bathroom with a super deep tub and shower combo and is drenched with light from the South facing windows. Across the hall are two more generously sized bedrooms that share a hallway bath. Central heat and air will keep this home cozy in the winter & cool during the summer. With everything so new, no need to worry about big expenses or updates looming ahead, move right in and enjoy the low maintenance. All appliances and even the washer and dryer stay. This small community of 7 new homes in the highly desirable River Road area is tucked back off the main road and includes a shared gazebo and outdoor entertaining space, lots of room for guests to park, and has a greenbelt and seasonal creek running along side it with a walking path. BONUS: FHA mortgage may be assumable, so you could get it for only 3.25% with a large down, ask for more details!
